
'''''Ntabwo ndi Umurozi''''' ni filime yikinamico yakozwe mu 2017 ku rwego mpuzamahanga yanditswe kandi iyobowe na Rungano Nyoni muri filime ye ya mbere<ref>I Am Not a Witch review – magical surrealism | World cinema | The Guardian</ref>. Yerekanwe mu gice cy’abayobozi ba Fortnight mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2017 kandi yegukana igihembo cya BAFTA kubera igihembo cyambere cyatanzwe n’umwanditsi w’Umwongereza<ref name=":0">I Am Not a Witch - Rotten Tomatoes <nowiki>https://www.rottentomatoes.com</nowiki> › m › i_am_not_a_witch</ref><ref>I Am Not a Witch movie review (2018) | Roger Ebert <nowiki>https://www.rogerebert.com</nowiki> › reviews › i-am-not-a-witc...</ref>, Umuyobozi cyangwa Producer wa Nyoni hamwe na producer Emily Morgan mu bihembo bya 71 bya Filime by’Abongereza<ref>How 'I Am Not a Witch' Is Transforming Zambia's Film Industry <nowiki>https://www.indiewire.com</nowiki> › 2018/09 › i-am-not-a-witc...</ref><ref>Review: I Am Not a Witch - Film Comment <nowiki>https://www.filmcomment.com</nowiki> › article › review-i-am-...</ref> .    Yatoranijwe  muri Filime Nziza Y’ururimi rw’amahanga mu bihembo bya 91 bya Academy, ariko ntabwo yatowe<ref>Review: In 'I Am Not a Witch,' Accusations and Tourism in Zambia <nowiki>https://www.nytimes.com</nowiki> › 2018/09/06 › movies › i-am-n...</ref>.  

