== Umusaruro ==
Umwanditsi-umuyobozi Rungano Nyoni yakuye igitekerezo mu nkuru zifatika zo gushinja abarozi muri Zambiya. Mu bushakashatsi yakoze kuri iyo filimi, yagiye muri [[Gana]] kandi amara igihe mu nkambi y’abapfumu, yitegereza ubuzima bwabo bwa buri munsi n'imigenzo yabo<ref>I Am Not A Witch: Nominations and awards <nowiki>https://envelope.latimes.com</nowiki> › awards › titles › i-am-not...</ref><ref>Rungano Nyoni's “I Am Not a Witch” Is UK's 2019 Foreign ... <nowiki>https://womenandhollywood.com</nowiki> › rungano-nyonis-i-a...</ref>.  

